ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would only recommend this course to graduate students who plan to work in this field, and it might be okay as an introduction for undergraduates.
fundamental for anyone studying galaxies. definitely recommended.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course might help me understand more in some of the colloquia in this department, but I don't work in this field so it won't contribute to my research.
This course is very relevant for anyone who is planning to study galaxies. Very useful for building a "big picture".
